description: We specialize in bringing the ballpark to our customers in our authentic Fenway Sausage. We also carry other sausage varieties that are sure to blow your mind. Choose one of our 1/2 lb. Burgers, 1/2 lb. All Beef Hot Dog, a Bourbon Steak Tip Sub, or maybe an Authentic Fenway Sausage Sandwich. We only carry the highest quality food at a fair price, and we would love to show you what we have to offer!!
name: Fenway Sausage Works
